程序包的使用
org.diku.dms.bds_project

  • 使用org.diku.dms.bds_project的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.diku.dms.bds_project  
    org.diku.dms.bds_project.query  
  • org.diku.dms.bds_project使用的org.diku.dms.bds_project中的类 
    类 说明
    Edge
    An edge consists of the id of source vertex, the id of destination vertex and the attribute on the edge.
    EdgeDirection  
    EdgePartition
    EdgePartition stores a collection of edges.
    EdgeRDD
    An RDD that exposes the interfaces to others as storing a collection of edges.
    EdgeTriplet
    An edge triplet consists of source vertex id, source vertex attribute, destination vertex id, destination vertex attribute and edge attribute
    EdgeTripletPartition
    EdgeTripletPartition stores a collections of EdgeTriplet.
    EdgeTripletRDD
    An RDD that stores a collection of edge triplets with interface for the data type as `EdgeTriplet`.
    Graph
    Graph consists of three RDDs: `VertexRDD`, `EdgeRDD` and `EdgeTripletRDD`.
    PartitionId
    PartitionId encapsulates the id of a partition in an RDD.
    RoutingTablePartition
    RoutingTablePartition encapsulates a routing table according to each vertex partition.
    VertexId
    VertexId encapsulates the id of a vertex which is a long.
    VertexIdToIndexMap
    A bijection map between vertex ids and the index (offset in some data structure).
    VertexPartition
    A `VertexPartition` stores a collection of vertices.
    VertexRDD
    An RDD that exposes the interfaces as storing a collection of vertices (a tuple of vertex id and vertex attribute).
